            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Shiori 0.9 - Initial Sparkle Update Setup</h2>
                <h3>What's New</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Sparkle Update Integration:</strong> Shiori now supports automatic updates via the Sparkle framework.</li>
                    <li><strong>Manual Update Check:</strong> Check for updates directly from the app menu bar.</li>
                    <li><strong>About Integration:</strong> About screen shows current version and update actions.</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Notes</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Release process is now standardized with versioned DMG assets on GitHub Releases.</li>
                    <li>Update feed and release notes are hosted via GitHub Pages.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
